1
00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:05,950
Operator: "GPS failed under the tunnel."

2
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:08,349
Black Box checked the recording.

3
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:10,949
That story is wrong.

4
00:00:10,750 --> 00:00:16,699
Hours of video, lidar, telemetry, controller logs.

5
00:00:16,750 --> 00:00:23,699
Evidence exists. Forensic review is still manual.

6
00:00:23,750 --> 00:00:28,699
One real driving session. No labels.

7
00:00:28,750 --> 00:00:34,700
Operator's note: check the tunnel.

8
00:00:34,750 --> 00:00:37,700
Not a one-shot summary.

9
00:00:37,750 --> 00:00:40,700
Opus 4.7 runs as a managed forensic agent.

10
00:00:40,750 --> 00:00:43,700
Tools, memory, streaming events.

11
00:00:43,750 --> 00:00:51,700
Project memory carries forward across runs.

12
00:00:51,750 --> 00:00:54,700
Doesn't send every frame.

13
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:57,700
Telemetry selects suspicious windows.

14
00:00:57,750 --> 00:01:05,700
High-res visual mining checks relevant cameras.

15
00:01:05,500 --> 00:01:08,950
The tunnel mildly degraded GNSS.

16
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,950
But the RTK heading failure started

17
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:13,450
43 minutes earlier.

18
00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:16,450
Drive-by-wire was never engaged.

19
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:20,450
The tunnel could not have caused this.

20
00:01:20,500 --> 00:01:24,950
Verdict: operator hypothesis refuted.

21
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:29,450
Cause sits lower in the stack.

22
00:01:29,500 --> 00:01:32,450
Operator hypothesis: refuted.

23
00:01:32,500 --> 00:01:36,450
Moving-base antenna: healthy.

24
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:40,450
Rover: never receives valid RTK heading.

25
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:44,450
Correction path broken before leaving the lot.

26
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:47,450
carr=NONE 100%. REL_POS_VALID never set.

27
00:01:47,500 --> 00:01:52,450
Findings written to a forensic report.

28
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:56,950
Output isn't a report — it's a scoped patch.

29
00:01:57,000 --> 00:02:01,450
RTCM message IDs. UART link check.

30
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:05,450
Plus a human-review gate.

31
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:08,449
Black Box proposes. Engineer approves.

32
00:02:10,150 --> 00:02:13,099
Opus 4.7 vs 4.6, same benchmark slice.

33
00:02:13,150 --> 00:02:16,099
Same accuracy. Better judgment.

34
00:02:16,150 --> 00:02:22,099
4.7 sees fine visual details 4.6 loses.

35
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:26,099
On under-specified cases, 4.7 abstains.

36
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:32,099
Not a single-car demo.

37
00:02:32,150 --> 00:02:36,099
More cars. A robotic boat.

38
00:02:36,150 --> 00:02:40,099
Clean recordings and injected failures.

39
00:02:40,150 --> 00:02:44,599
When evidence is weak, it refuses to invent a bug.

40
00:02:44,650 --> 00:02:49,099
No evidence. No claim.

41
00:02:48,900 --> 00:02:51,849
Open benchmark. Reproducible runs.

42
00:02:51,900 --> 00:02:54,849
Robot forensics in minutes, for cents.
